{"tid":1647834,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"到底發夢食煙係咩心態？","createTime":"2019-10-12T02:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T00:56:20.000Z","uid":309825,"like":74,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"0a53234c7fc52c88d4c35db4bef5f1e8e48a8461","tid":1647834,"uid":309825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:22:57.000Z","msg":"我講梗唔係tg嗰啲煙<br />\n係真係cigarette嗰啲煙<br />\n<br />\n有時發夢中途 有啲時間大家坐底休息梗<br />\n點知有啲煙飄過嚟<br />\n成日以為係tg 原來只係隔離有手足食煙<br />\n<br />\n我明白煙民壓力大<br />\n要靠chur支煙減下壓<br />\n不過吸煙危害健康<br />\n到時睇唔到光復香港唔好喊啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以都係戒煙啦<br />\n<br />\n忠言一定逆耳㗎喇<br />\n等同林鄭都唔鐘意聽到人勸佢收手一樣<br />\n不過去到將來就會知道邊個有道理㗎喇"},{"pid":"544fc949b9052cb16710fcaeb1a8c7ea704698bf","tid":1647834,"uid":306337,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:26:08.000Z","msg":"咁大壓力嘛 食兩支冷靜啲 我係前線都啪返支先上<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好當我係失敗撚 唔該入嚟睇一睇 然後諗一諗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n革命已完 大家可以準備奶共啦 因為香港人唔諗住贏.<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1647805\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1647805</a>"},{"pid":"61a10414b963130cd4ca79d657e5e61571688418","tid":1647834,"uid":303124,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:26:49.000Z","msg":"場運動因為你地亂搞活動就黎要輸喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1647794\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1647794</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6e1501c7bfe44e0a2d28740222f2a88cdf1c8bca","tid":1647834,"uid":12696,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:27:32.000Z","msg":"應該會有手足答你<br />\nDllm 吊頸都要抖氣啦<br />\nChur枝煙又屌洗死阿"},{"pid":"4f380c70680cc93fa58d4fb892b06cd3d942865b","tid":1647834,"uid":370,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e1501c7bfe44e0a2d28740222f2a88cdf1c8bca","tid":1647834,"uid":12696,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:27:32.000Z","msg":"應該會有手足答你<br />\nDllm 吊頸都要抖氣啦<br />\nChur枝煙又屌洗死阿"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"